%202%2010%202a510%20510%200%200073%2016l16%204%203%201c1%201%2013%203%2014%202l2%201%208%202%2010%203%208%201%208%202c4%202%2014%202%2016%201%202-3%200-4-6-5l-5-1c-1-2%202-2%2011%200%208%201%208%201%2012-1l4-2%201-1%206-2a146%20146%200%200114-8l4-2%205-2c0-1%201-2%203-2l2-3c-1-3-10-6-13-4h-2c-1-2-8-3-13-4h-4c-4-2-9-3-12-2l-4-1-7-2-9-2-10-2-6-1c0-1-11-3-13-2l-2-1-12-3-9-1-7-1-2-1-13-3h-3c-2-1-11-3-12-2l-2-1-13-3-3-1-8-1-5-1-4-1c-2%200-2%200%200%201h-3l-6-1-8-2c-7%200-7%200-4%201M47%20142l-11%204-8%203-3%201c-3%201-4%204-2%205%203%202%2017%200%2017-2%200-1%203-3%208-4l5-5c0-3-2-4-6-2m137%200l-1%201c-5%200-4%202%201%203h9l4-1-2%201-2%202%205%201c4%201%206%201%209-1l4-1-3-1-6-1-2-1-2-1-8-1c-5-2-6-2-6%200m-8%2014l-4%203%207%201c7%202%207%202%2012%200l5-2-4-2c-8-2-11-2-16%200m19%204c-6%203-5%203%2011%206%2044%2010%2045%2010%2040%207l-2-1%201-1c-1-1%200-1%201-1a1716%201716%200%2001-45-11c-1-1-4%200-6%201\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/277cf/portada.webp 310w,\n/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/5077d/portada.webp 620w,\n/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/e1adb/portada.webp 1240w,\n/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/92eb6/portada.webp 1860w,\n/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/e2cdc/portada.webp 2265w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/b0751/portada.jpg 310w,\n/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/e1d7b/portada.jpg 620w,\n/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/d1f04/portada.jpg 1240w,\n/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/5759f/portada.jpg 1860w,\n/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/45e7e/portada.jpg 2265w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/6efacf0f03140b0eaeba1d4dff290446/d1f04/portada.jpg\"\n          alt=\"portada\"\n          title=\"portada\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Our goal at Perf.Reviews is to show the importance of web performance. Why?</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Little knowledge about the developer tools included in the browser</strong>. These tools are very powerful and are usually enough to find and correct most problems, yet most of their features are not known by most developers.</li>\n<li><strong>Catching up on best practices in web performance is costly, in time and money</strong>. It requires a lot of reading news on updates and putting them into practice.\nWhat is a good practice today may not be tomorrow. Some examples are <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yURLTwZ3ehk\">the combination of static assets, domain sharding, and inlining</a>, or <a href=\"https://csswizardry.com/2019/05/self-host-your-static-assets/\">using CDNs to host your own static resources</a>. Last, but not least, take into consideration the balance between feature support, browser market share and the cost of polyfills.</li>\n<li><strong>Finding performance problems is difficult</strong> without knowing the details of how the network protocols work, how the browser prioritizes requests and parses its result or what the cost of executing JS or processing an image is.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCNoF5_1loBFvW2lZXPxp8ww\">Our videos</a> and <a href=\"/\">articles</a> try to answer these problems with practical examples. We show the potential of both browser and third-party tools, and use them to find problems in real sites.</p>\n<h2 id=\"blogs-and-twitter\">Blogs and Twitter</h2>\n<p>One of the best ways to stay up to date is to follow the blogs and Twitter accounts of browsers and developers who advocate for creating fast sites.</p>\n<p>We have compiled <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jmperezperez/lists/web-perf\">a list on Twitter with the main accounts</a>, and it is always a good idea to subscribe to the blogs authored by <a href=\"https://addyosmani.com/blog/\">Addy Osmani</a>, <a href=\"https://dougsillars.com/blog/\">Doug Sillars</a>, <a href=\"https://www.filamentgroup.com/lab/\">Filament Group</a>, <a href=\"https://csswizardry.com/\">Harry Roberts</a> and <a href=\"https://timkadlec.com/remembers/\">Tim Kadlec</a> amongst others.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1240px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/1b29a/filament-group.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 74.8189863234111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'299\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M0%2026l1%2026%2015%203a1411%201411%200%2000290%2011l94-6%201-31V0H0v26\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/277cf/filament-group.webp 310w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/5077d/filament-group.webp 620w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/e1adb/filament-group.webp 1240w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/92eb6/filament-group.webp 1860w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/d232f/filament-group.webp 2480w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/e669c/filament-group.webp 2486w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/fa223/filament-group.png 310w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/a5ed1/filament-group.png 620w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/7bfa5/filament-group.png 1240w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/b429f/filament-group.png 1860w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/d03be/filament-group.png 2480w,\n/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/1b29a/filament-group.png 2486w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/80036ed330842f4ecc27ac606c99a1f6/7bfa5/filament-group.png\"\n          alt=\"Filament Group&#39;s blog is a good resource about CSS loading techniques and sources\"\n          title=\"Filament Group&#39;s blog is a good resource about CSS loading techniques and sources\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Filament Group&#39;s blog is a good resource about CSS loading techniques and sources</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>One of the best resources to learn about web performance is <a href=\"https://web.dev/learn\">Web.dev</a>.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1240px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e1b8e99452896df67ee273429c5bde64/04a3c/google-web-dev-learn.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.34841628959275%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/20