\n<p>This site from Google collects information that was previously dispersed in different sites and is now consolidated through practical guides.</p>\n<h2 id=\"tools\">Tools</h2>\n<p>To detect performance problems the best approach is to run a web audit. From within the browser <a href=\"https://perf.reviews/tools/1.2-Interpretando-Lighthouse-Performance/\">it is possible to perform a quick check</a>, and there are also websites like <a href=\"https://%20web.dev/measure\">web.dev/measure</a> that generate a detailed report of the performance of a particular URL.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1240px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/fc364/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.07866507747319%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'224\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M199%207c0%206%200%207-2%207l-2%201h4v105l1%20105V112a6334%206334%200%2000-1-105M87%2037c-2%200-1%206%201%206%202%201%203%201%204-1l1-1c0%204%206%204%207%200%201-2%201-2%201%201%201%202%204%202%205%200%200-1%200-2-2-3-1-1-1-1%201-1v-1H95c-1%201-1%201%201%201h3l-3%201-4-1c-1-2-2-2-5-1m209%2021c-3%201-6%206-6%2010%200%2011%2015%2014%2020%204%204-8-5-18-14-14m-3%204c-4%206-1%2013%206%2015%209%201%2015-11%207-16-4-3-9-2-13%201m-129%2046l-1%207v6h30v-13l-15-1-14%201\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/277cf/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 310w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/5077d/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 620w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/e1adb/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 1240w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/92eb6/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 1860w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/d232f/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 2480w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/d75f7/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.webp 3356w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/fa223/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 310w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/a5ed1/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 620w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/7bfa5/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 1240w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/b429f/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 1860w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/d03be/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 2480w,\n/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/fc364/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png 3356w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/6181be45a2233a4d686ff4a42c7cd09e/7bfa5/google-web-lighthouse-perf-reviews.png\"\n          alt=\"Performance report of perf.reviews using the online version of Lighthouse at https://web.dev/measure. Overview and report view.\"\n          title=\"Performance report of perf.reviews using the online version of Lighthouse at https://web.dev/measure. Overview and report view.\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Performance report of perf.reviews using the online version of Lighthouse at https://web.dev/measure. Overview and report view.</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>A tool we recommend is <a href=\"https://webpagetest.org\">WebPageTest</a>, which is also useful to find performance problems. It is great for comparing multiple sites, and also to test variations customizing which browser, network speed, device and location to use when running the test.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1240px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/60120/webpagetest-filmstrip.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.24854530340815%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'269\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M0%20135v134h401V0H0v135m240-40v35l1-34V62h24l24-1h-49v34M41%2095v33h46V62H41v33m48%200v33h47V62H89v33m50%200v33h47V62h-47v33m51%200v33h47V62h-47v33m107-25l-4%207%202%204c2%204%204%205%207%203v-5c-4-7%200-15%206-13%201%201%201%201-1%202-2%202-2%204%202%204l2%201-2%201-1%201%202%201%201%203c-1%205%200%206%205%206%204%200%204%200%207-4l2-4-4-7-3-7h-17l-4%207m51%200l-4%206%202%205c2%203%202%204%204%203%204-1%205-2%203-5-3-5-3-11%201-12%204-2%208%200%204%201-2%202-2%204%201%204l2%202h-1l-1%201%202%201v5c-1%202%201%204%206%204%204%200%204%200%207-4l2-4-4-7-4-6-8-1h-9l-3%207M138%20172v34h49v-34l-1-29v4h-47v-8h24l24-1h-49v34m51%200v34h49l-1-29v-30h-47v-8h24l24-1h-49v34m51%200v34h48v-59h-47v-8h24l24-1h-49v34m-199%200v33h46v-66H41v33m48%200v33h47v-66H89v33m68-19c-4%204-4%2011%202%2013%202%201%203%201%204-1s2-2%203-1c2%202%205-2%205-6%200-3-4-7-8-8-2%200-3%200-6%203m51%200c-4%204-4%208%200%2012%203%203%205%203%206%200%201-2%201-2%203-1%204%203%206-7%202-11-3-4-7-4-11%200m53-2c-4%202-5%204-5%208%200%205%207%2011%208%206l4-1c6%201%206-11-1-13h-6M41%20239l1%203h26v-5l-14-1H41v3\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/277cf/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 310w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/5077d/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 620w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/e1adb/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 1240w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/92eb6/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 1860w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/4f50c/webpagetest-filmstrip.webp 2406w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/fa223/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 310w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/a5ed1/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 620w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/7bfa5/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 1240w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/b429f/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 1860w,\n/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/60120/webpagetest-filmstrip.png 2406w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/148a50502cd2cec2509851427357171c/7bfa5/webpagetest-filmstrip.png\"\n          alt=\"Comparing two websites with WebPagetest, filmstrip view\"\n          title=\"Comparing two websites with WebPagetest, filmstrip view\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">Comparing two websites with WebPagetest, filmstrip view</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Through its advanced options you can also <a href=\"https://andydavies.me/blog/2018/02/19/using-webpagetest-to-measure-the-impact-of-3rd%20-party-tags/\">check the impact of 3rd party scripts</a>, simulate <a href=\"http://blog.patrickmeenan.com/2011/10/testing-for-frontend-spof.html\">single point of failures (SPOF)</a> and <a href=\"https://deanhume.com/ten-things-you-didnt-know-about-webpagetest-org/\">much more</a>. It even <a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/use-webpagetest-api/\">has an API</a> that lets to run all this from a script or integrate it in a build and deployment pipeline.</p>\n<p>Other tools analyze periodically a site and can alert us when any of the metrics worsens substantially, below a certain threshold. We recommend <a href=\"https://calibreapp.com\">Calibre</a>, <a href=\"https://www.debugbear.com\">DebugBear</a>, <a href=\"https://www.sitespeed.io/\">SiteSpeed</a> and <a href=\"https://speedcurve.com/\">SpeedCurve</a>.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1240px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/200b774a1d4efe55b294d08e369fb2da/f7947/speedcurve-guardian.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.517774343122106%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'182\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M0%2091v91h401V0H0v91m10-53c-2%201-1%202%201%202s2%200%201%202c-2%203-2%205-1%205l4-3c2-4%203-4%202-1%200%203%203%205%206%203%202%200%202-1%202-3v-2l1%204c0%202%204%203%206%201%203-3%201-9-3-9l-3%202h-2c-2-2-13-2-14-1m25%200c-2%201-1%209%201%209l1-2h2c3%203%205%202%203-2-1-1-2-2-1-3%202-2%203-1%203%203s0%204%203%204c4%200%205-1%205-5%200-3-1-4-2-5-4%20