%202%203%205%204%208%202%202-1%203-6%201-8-2-1-7-2-10-1M261%2088c0%202-1%202-11%202s-10%201-10%203c0%201%200%202%2010%202s11%200%2011%202c0%201%201%202%203%202s2%200%202-6c0-7%200-7-2-7s-3%201-3%202m109%202c0%202%201%202%206%202%206%200%207%200%208%202%201%203%200%203-8%203-6-1-6%200-6%202s0%202%207%202c5%200%207%200%207%202l2%201%202-1%202-2%203%202c2%202%204%201%204-1%200-3-2-4-6-5-3-1-3-1-3-5v-4h-9c-8%200-9%200-9%202M80%20101v7a3949%203949%200%20010-7m181%201c0%201-1%202-11%202h-10v2c0%202%200%203%2010%203s11%200%2011%202c0%201%201%202%203%202s2%200%202-6c0-7%200-7-2-7s-3%201-3%202m111%203c-2%201-3%206%200%208l7%201c8%200%2012-5%207-8-3-2-12-3-14-1m-133%2012l2%202h4l4%204c7%208%2017%204%2017-7v-2h-27v3m131%201c0%202%201%203%207%203%205%200%207%200%207%202%201%201%200%202-7%201-7%200-7%200-7%203%200%202%200%202%207%202%209%200%209%202%200%202-6%200-7%201-7%202s1%202%207%202c9%200%209%202%200%202-6%200-7%200-7%202s1%202%208%202l9-1%201-12v-11l-9-1c-9%200-9%200-9%202m-133%2011c0%202%201%203%2014%205%2016%204%2016%204%2016%201a750%20750%200%2000-30-6m2%2014c0%205%200%205%203%205l2-2%202-2%205%202c9%205%2018%200%2014-7-1-2-4%200-4%202%200%203-3%203-8%200l-9-3h-5v5m134%200c-3%202-4%202-4%206%201%202%201%203%208%203%209%200%2011-1%2011-5-1-3-3-4-4-1v2l-2-2c-3-3-7-4-9-3m-3%2013c-1%202%201%203%208%203%208%200%207%201-2%201-6%200-6%201-6%203%200%201%200%202%208%202%209%200%2010-1%2010-7v-3l-9-1c-8%200-9%200-9%202m-130%204c-2%201-1%202%203%202l5%201-5%201c-6%203-5%204%205%204%2010-1%2012-2%205-3h-3l4-2%203-3h-17m-1%2013l2%202v2c-4%203-1%203%207%202%2013-2%2013-3%202-6h-11m133%204c-2%201-4%205-2%206h2c2-3%203-2%206%201%204%204%2011%202%2010-3-1-4-10-6-16-4m-131%206c-2%202-3%205-1%205l2-2c3-3%2012-3%2013%201%202%203%200%204-8%204-6%200-8%200-8%202l8%201c6%200%208%200%208%202l2%201c1%200%201-12-1-14s-13-2-15%200m128%2017c-1%202%201%203%205%203h5l-5%202c-7%203-6%204%203%204h10l1-1c0-2-1-2-4-2h-4l4-2c5-3%205-3%203-4h-18m-128%203c-5%204-1%208%208%208%208%200%2012-3%208-7-3-2-13-2-16-1m-2%2012l5%201h5l-5%202-4%203c0%201%2017%201%2018-1l-5-1h-5l5-2c7-3%206-4-5-4-7%200-9%200-9%202\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/277cf/books.webp 310w,\n/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/5077d/books.webp 620w,\n/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/e1adb/books.webp 1240w,\n/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/d90da/books.webp 1678w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/b0751/books.jpg 310w,\n/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/e1d7b/books.jpg 620w,\n/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/d1f04/books.jpg 1240w,\n/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/da229/books.jpg 1678w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/e3b60bb9f8d62e8631b665c658fbf638/d1f04/books.jpg\"\n          alt=\"These are some of the most popular web performance books, published between 2008 and 2019\"\n          title=\"These are some of the most popular web performance books, published between 2008 and 2019\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">These are some of the most popular web performance books, published between 2008 and 2019</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Even so, we want to recommend books that can help you get a good foundation in web performance optimization:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.manning.com/books/web-performance-in-action\">Web Performance in Action</a></strong>, written by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/malchata\">Jeremy L. Wagner</a>. It is focused on web performance in general, covering the use of tools, CSS, JS and images optimization, loading of resources in an effective way, improving performance using Service Workers and an overview of the HTTP/2 protocol. A lot of information gathered through many sources that make this a great book..</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/High-Performance-Mobile-Web-Optimizing/dp/1491912553\">High Performance Mobile Web: Best Practices for Optimizing Mobile Web Apps</a></strong>, written by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/firt\">Maximiliano Firtman</a>. It is focused on web performance on mobile devices. It start by introducing the mobile web, how to measure performance, and how to optimize first and subsequent visits using tools like Service Workers. He also talks about Responsive Web Design and writes a chapter called Extreme Mobile Web Performance dedicated to specific tips to improve the performance of our websites for those devices.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>It is a book to keep in mind, since we are at a time where most sites are <strong>Mobile First</strong> and even also some others that are <strong>Mobile Only</strong>.</p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/High-Performance-Browser-Networking-performance/dp/1449344763/ref=sr_1_1\">High Performance Browser Networking: What every web developer should know about networking and web performance</a></strong>, the subtitle that adds <a href=\"https://twitter.com/igrigorik\">Ilya Grigorik</a> to this book is “What every web developer should know about networks and web performance”. Very interesting content that teaches us about bandwidth, latency, TCP and UDP blocks, TSL, and WiFi and mobile data network. It touches on the HTTP/1.X and HTTP/2 protocols and explains how to optimize the delivery of assets on those. The last part of the book covers XMLHttpRequest, CORS, Server-Send Events, WebSockets, and WebRTC.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>A must-read book for those who want to learn more about networks and their relation to performance. This book is also available online for free on <a href=\"https://hpbn.co\">hpbn.co</a>.</p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Using-WebPageTest-Performance-Testing-Novices/dp/1491902590\">Using WebPageTest: Web Performance Testing for Novices and Power Users</a></strong>, this time we recommend a book on a tool, <strong>the tool</strong> for many people. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rick_viscomi\">Rick Viscomi</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/andydavies\">Andy Davies</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcelduran\">Marcel Duran</a> presents this 3-part book: Basic, Intermediate and Advanced. It explains how to use WebPageTest to detect what slows down a web, settings for mobile devices, scripting and how to integrate WebPageTest with a continuous integration tool through their API. In the last chapter they show us how to implement WebPageTest in our own private instance.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/High-Performance-Images-Shrink-Deliver-ebook/dp/B01MG9CFXG\">High Performance Images: Shrink, Load, and Deliver Images for Speed</a></strong>, this is Joan’s favorite. Written by several authors, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/colinbendell\">Colin Bendell</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tkadlec\">Tim Kadlec</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/yoavweiss\">Yoav Weiss</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/guypod\">Guy Podjarny</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/njdoyle\">Nick Doyle</a> and Mike McCall offer us in-depth knowledge about images on the web. Starting with the theory of digital images, the different compression formats (lossy and lossless), SVG optimization, lazy loading, image processing at the GPU level, an efficient way to deliver our images to the browser and how to implement our own flow to optimize the images automatically.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>There is also <a href=\"https://content.akamai.com/pg6293-high-performance-images-ebook.html\">a free version available in PDF</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"personalized-audits-and-training\">Personalized audits and training</h2>\n<p>We are aware that it is difficult for development teams to gain expertise on web performance and adopt a performance culture. Through our <a href=\"https://perf.reviews/en/services/\">customized workshop and audit services</a> we help companies understand the issues on their websites and take the right steps to fix and avoid them in the future.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to keep up to date on web performance","date":"August 09, 2019","description":"Tips and resources to learn about web performance. Tools, websites and developers who write about new techniques and APIs to create sites that load fast and are data conscious.","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/785076bd1a8e6bcc85b2f2fffef9ac88/e9c7b/featured-image.png","srcSet":"/static/785076bd1a8e6bcc85b2f2fffef9ac88/69781/featured-image.png 250w,\n/static/785076bd1a8e6bcc85b2f2fffef9ac88/3fa08/featured-image.png 500w,\n/static/785076bd1a8e6bcc85b2f2fffef9ac88/e9c7b/featured-image.png 1000w,\n/static/785076bd1a8e6bcc85b2f2fffef9ac88/a4fe2/featured-image.png 1500w,\n/static/785076bd1a8e6bcc85b2f2fffef9ac88/dc9f7/featured-image.png 2000w,\n/static/785076bd1a8e6bcc85b2f2fffef9ac88/c81f1/featured-image.png 2134w","sizes":"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/blog/mantenerse-al-dia/en/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/mantenerse-al-dia/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Cómo mantenerse al día sobre rendimiento web"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/video-en-la-web/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"El formato vídeo en la web"}}}}}